#Prayer (see "Hymn to Leibowitz" by W. Miller, page 22)
### {120}{}{...Let's start the prayer, brothers and sisters!}
{120}{}{…让我们开始祈祷吧，兄弟姐妹们！ -- ...Let's start the prayer, brothers and sisters!}
