{124}{}{从瘟疫，饥荒和战争，神圣的火焰，拯救我们。 -- From plague, famine and wars, Holy Fire, deliver us.}
### {125}{}{From the epicenter and hypocenter, Holy Fire, deliver us.}
{125}{}{从震中和震源，神圣之火，拯救我们。 -- From the epicenter and hypocenter, Holy Fire, deliver us.}
