{126}{}{来自钴雨，神圣之火，拯救我们。 -- From the rain of cobalt, Holy Fire, deliver us.}
### {127}{}{From the rain of strontium, Holy Fire, deliver us.}
{127}{}{来自锶雨，神圣之火，拯救我们。 -- From the rain of strontium, Holy Fire, deliver us.}
### {128}{}{From the precipitation of caesium, Holy Fire, deliver us.}
{128}{}{从铯的沉淀中，神圣之火，拯救我们。 -- From the precipitation of caesium, Holy Fire, deliver us.}
### {129}{}{From the curse of Radiation, Holy Fire, deliver us.}
{129}{}{从辐射的诅咒，神圣的火焰，拯救我们。 -- From the curse of Radiation, Holy Fire, deliver us.}
### {130}{}{From the conception of monsters, Holy Fire, deliver us.}
{130}{}{从怪物的概念来看，神圣之火，拯救我们。 -- From the conception of monsters, Holy Fire, deliver us.}
### {131}{}{From the curse of Mutation, Holy Fire, deliver us.}
{131}{}{从突变的诅咒，神圣的火焰，拯救我们。 -- From the curse of Mutation, Holy Fire, deliver us.}
